{
  "stem": "20581.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, I knew them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember their name, but I knew them all, sure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it was a small town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was one-- one know the other one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By the way, you're talking about these pogroms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got to mention one story also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because you were asking about the neighbors, or about the kids [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, in the Jewish religion, you're not allowed to do any cooking or to light any candles after Shabbos, during the Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we used to have one guy who used to come around in the whole town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was what they call him, the Shabbos goy He was the one who would go in and put on the fires.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because we had no electricity and no water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he used to be the one who used to come in on Saturday morning and put on the fire for the stove and for the oven.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everybody, Monday, they used to pay him a few pennies, a few zloties, whatever, some food and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was helping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This was going on all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When the Germans came in, he was the one who was that got-- he decided who shall live who shall die.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When the Germans lined up all these people the first time, and they took all the men and they lined them up in the center of town, and they asked-- his name was a-- a Ukrainian name.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "His name was Yaska Volk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was the one, like he would tell you, this one goes on this side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the other one goes on this side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this one goes on this side, and this one goes on this side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was the selector.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
